Implements a Perceptron model to learn logical AND gate behavior using supervised learning classification method.
from sklearn.linear_model import Perceptron

# AND Gate Data
X = [[0,0],[0,1],[1,0],[1,1]]
y = [0,0,0,1]

model = Perceptron()
model.fit(X, y)

print("Prediction:", model.predict([[1,1]]))

OUTPUT-Prediction: [1]
